On the desk there is:\n\n[[>> A small bell|bell]].\n[[>> A folded note|note1]].\n\nNow that you think about it, using the [[bathroom|GFwc2]] seems like a good idea.\n<<endif>>
\nYou ping the small bell with all your might.\n\nNothing happens.\nYou ping the bell again.\n\nThe loud voice says:\n<em>"Keep the noise down young PLANKTON, will you?".</em>\n\n[[Go back.|Reception]]
\nYou see the thunder storm getting closer. Rain is running down the outside of the glass.\n\n
